                        <p>
                            <span class="fsf-24">Special Lecture by JEON Yootaek (Pyongyang University of Science &amp; Tecnology)</span><br />
                            North Korean Higher Education and Education at PUST
                        </p>
                    </dt>
                    <dd class="con">                       
                        <p class="mt-20">2018.02.23 16:00 - 18:00</p>                        
                        <div class="view_gall mtb50">
